These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, bolivar, oliveros
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, horse, fish
City: berlin, boston, hannover
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, tram, skateboard
3 different games are played: backgammon, billiard, domino
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: horror, documentary, sports
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: tennis, water-polo, weightlifting
 1. the person who's sport is tennis is the person watching documentary movies##1
 2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person driving the skateboard##1
 3. the oliveros-smoker is between the person watching sports movies and the bolivar-smoker##2
 4. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
 5. the person driving the tram is the owner of the fish##1
 6. the person traveling to hannover is the person watching horror movies##1
 7. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 8. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
 9. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
10. the person traveling to boston is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Cigar      | bolivar    | oliveros   | blend           |
| Pet          | horse       | fish    | chinchilla         |
| City         | boston    | hannover  | berlin        |
| Transport           | trike | tram   | skateboard      |
| Game   | billiard        | domino    | backgammon       |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary     | horror  | sports       |
| Sport         | tennis     | water-polo | weightlifting |

