The people have 3 different jobs:  fisherman, dressmaker, videographer
There are 3 different favourite colors: grey, yellow, coral
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, havana, siglo
3 different games are played: canasta, monopoly, go
3 different pets are kept: dog, horse, pony
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, april, february
 1. the owner of the pony is the person playing monopoly##1
 2. the owner of the pony is the person who likes coral##1
 3. the person who likes coral is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in december is between the tower house and the futuristic house##2
 5. the person playing go is on the far left##1
 6. the tower house is the oliveros-smoker##1
 7. the havana-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 8. the fisherman is the person who likes grey##1
 9. the person who likes coral is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
10. the owner of the pony is on the left of the videographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| House      | futuristic   | wooden    | tower         |
| Job          | fisherman    | dressmaker | videographer          |
| Color   | grey  | coral  | yellow     |
| Cigar   | siglo       | havana      | oliveros         |
| Game   | go      | monopoly   | canasta    |
| Pet           | dog        | pony      | horse         |
| Birthday         | april | december  | february |

