.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-17::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, disco, r&b
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, hiking, singing
3 different games are played: scrabble, chess, whist
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, october, july
The people have 3 different jobs:  designer, paramedic, dressmaker
City: prague, rome, nizza
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, daffodil, orchid
 1. the person traveling to nizza is in the middle##1
 2. the fan of disco is in the middle##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 4. the person who's hobby is singing is the person playing chess##1
 5. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 6. the dressmaker is on the left of the person playing chess##1
 7. the person who growsorchid is between the fan of electronic and the person who's birthday is in january##2
 8. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
 9. the person playing chess is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
10. the dressmaker is on the left of the paramedic##1
11. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Music-Genre      | electronic | disco      | r&b      |
| Hobby         | drawing     | hiking     | singing  |
| Game   | whist | scrabble  | chess |
| Birthday   | october  | july     | january |
| Job           | designer        | dressmaker | paramedic     |
| City         | prague    | nizza | rome   |
| Flower     | daffodil        | orchid        | balloon-flower   |

