.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-18::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, juice, milk
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, egyptian, spanish
There are 3 different favourite colors: fuchsia, ivory, apricot
3 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, rabbit, horse
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: bellflower, sunflower, aconite
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, dannemann, ritmeester
3 different games are played: bridge, monopoly, whist
1. the person drinking juice is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
2. the person playing whist is on the right of the spanish##1
3. the egyptian is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
4. the blend-smoker is between the person who growsbellflower and the owner of the rabbit##2
5. the spanish is between the owner of the horse and the person who likes apricot##2
6. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the spanish##1
7. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
8. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
9. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
| Beverage      | fanta      | juice      | milk       |
| Nationality          | egyptian      | spanish    | colombian   |
| Color         | apricot    | fuchsia     | ivory     |
| Pet           | rabbit    | guinea-pig | horse   |
| Flower   | sunflower    | aconite    | bellflower       |
| Cigar         | ritmeester | blend      | dannemann    |
| Game     | monopoly       | bridge | whist |

