.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-19::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, fanta
City: san-francisco, prague, marseilles
There are 3 different nationalities: american, australian, italian
There are 3 different favourite colors: lavender, emerald, orange
3 different games are played: bridge, billiard, scrabble
The people have 3 different jobs:  writer, firefighter, paramedic
3 different pets are kept: lizard, goldfish, rabbit
1. the owner of the goldfish is the australian##1
2. the firefighter is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
3. the paramedic is on the right of the firefighter##1
4. the person who likes orange is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
5. the person traveling to prague is between the person drinking fanta and the american##2
6. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
7. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
8. the owner of the lizard is the person who likes orange##1
9. the american is on the right of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |
| Beverage      | fanta       | coffee     | cola         |
| City          | san-francisco     | prague      | marseilles     |
| Nationality         | australian | italian    | american      |
| Color   | lavender   | emerald | orange    |
| Game   | billiard        | scrabble     | bridge   |
| Job         | writer     | firefighter | paramedic |
| Pet     | goldfish     | rabbit       | lizard    |

