.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-20::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, february, april
There 3 different types of food: broccoli, spinach, zucchini
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, horror, spy
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: hip-hop, disco, ambient
There are 3 different favourite colors: azure, lavender, fuchsia
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: aconite, bellflower, amaryllis
The people have 3 different hobbies: photography, board-games, fishing
1. the person who's birthday is in march is the person eating zucchini##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person who growsaconite##1
3. the person watching animation movies is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who likes fuchsia##2
4. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
5. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
7. the person watching horror movies is the person eating broccoli##1
8. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
9. the fan of disco is between the person eating broccoli and the person who's hobby is photography##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Birthday      | february    | march       | april      |
| Food          | broccoli   | zucchini   | spinach  |
| Movie-Genre           | horror  | animation | spy    |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop   | disco     | ambient  |
| Color           | fuchsia     | azure        | lavender |
| Flower         | bellflower | aconite   | amaryllis  |
| Hobby     | board-games    | fishing     | photography      |

 